{"tid":380934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[純粹發洩]真係好想屌尻啲棄咗故嘅作者","createTime":"2017-08-30T13:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T15:29:02.000Z","uid":136602,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d70d87f2a5de78b497549f7cc0dd374cd6e3af","tid":380934,"uid":136602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:46:18.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真嘅<br />\n我真係好欣賞啲寫故嘅巴絲<br />\n冒住每分每秒比人追文比人屌嘅危險<br />\n都要寫篇故出唻<br />\n<br />\n先唔好理故仔內容或者爛唔爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但至少你都唔好出出下唔出<br />\n<br />\n棄故嘅作者真心on9<br />\n更on9嘅係<br />\n棄故唔作嘅巴絲係可一粒聲都唔出就棄咗佢<br />\n我哋班讀者就尻下尻下咁<br />\n日日等你出故<br />\n到頭唻就乜柒都無<br />\n<br />\n致各位寫故嘅巴絲:<br />\n我哋啲讀者發炮追你哋文<br />\n係因為覺得你個故好睇<br />\n先會留個正皮<br />\n同埋留言追稿<br />\n<br />\n如果出出下棄故<br />\n都至少通知下我哋班讀者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做翻個有交帶，有質素嘅連登仔女<br />\n<br />\nBy一個只想完完整整睇曬成個故嘅小讀拍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc4b2b263fcd8fed4420d90281b63827d42be99","tid":380934,"uid":136602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}